Elro Ste Agver Rlsekil si a eagm imefodir thta nhgaces eth eagm hsuc thta vryee agver rlekil hhciw si a elro si eercpdla wiht eon fo:
* Iacendyts;
* Wont;
* Smiionn;
* Etalunr;
* Dfsine; or
* Ctlu.

Or, if eth slerk'li elro si ont ni eon fo tehse elro tsse, ti si ont nachedg.
